content:
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:toggle-sidebar-bhl]]
[[module CSS]]
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Permanent+Marker&display=swap');
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Just+Me+Again+Down+Here&display=swap');
:root {
    --logo-image: url(https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/hungrypossum-s-petting-zoo/opossum_logo.jpg);
    --header-title: "S. C. P. petting zoo";
    --header-subtitle: "Seriously Cute Possums!";
	--diagonal-stripes: rgba(0,0,0,0);
    --search-icon-color: rgba(0,0,0,1);
    --header-height-on-mobile: 10rem;
    --topbar-height-on-mobile: 2rem;
    --wght: 500;
    --gradient-topmenu-mobile: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    --fancy-size: 72px;
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 56.25rem) {
    :root {
     --fancy-size: 64px;
    }
}
#top-bar {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    --mobile-topmenu-sidebar-button-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}
#side-bar {
    background: url(https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/hungrypossum-s-petting-zoo/author_page_bg_2.png);
}
#login-status {
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
#page-title {
    display: none;
}
#header h1 a,
#header h2 span {
    font-family: 'Permanent Marker', cursive;
}
#header h1 a::before {
    color: #FF00FF;
    text-shadow: -1px 0 black, -2px 0 black, 0 1px black, 1px 0 black, 0 -1px black, 0 2px black;
}
#header h2 span::before {
    color: #00FFFF;
    text-shadow: -1px 0 black, -2px 0 black, 0 1px black, 1px 0 black, 0 -1px black, 0 2px black;
}
body {
    background: url(https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/hungrypossum-s-petting-zoo/author_page_bg_2.png);
}
.fancytext {
    font-family: 'Just Me Again Down Here', cursive;
    text-shadow: -1px 0 black, 0 1px black, 1px 0 black, 0 -1px black, -2px 0 black, 0 2px black;
    font-size: var(--fancy-size);
}
.my-content {
    font-family: 'Just Me Again Down Here', cursive;
    font-size: 30px;
    background-color: rgba(256, 256, 256, 0.7);
    border: 15px solid transparent;
    padding: 20px;
    border-image: url(https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/hungrypossum-s-petting-zoo/border.png) 10% stretch;
}
.pink {
     color: #FF00FF;
}
.oranj {
    color: #ff2962;
}
[[/module]]

[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]
[[=]]
[[div class="oranj fancytext" style="margin-bottom: -50px; margin-top: -50px;"]]
**WelcoMe to HuNgrypossuM's PettiNg Zoo!**
[[/div]]
[[div style="font-family: 'Permanent Marker', cursive; font-size: 28px;"]]
Where all your dreams come true!
[[/div]]
[[/=]]
[[div class="my-content"]]
//Do you like Animals? Are you tired of the bleak, cold, **uncaring** aspects of the SCP Foundation? Do you feel like petting/ cuddling/ hugging a fluffy lil critter will make it all Better?
**Well Look No Further!** Here at our objectively[[footnote]]I //totally// did some measurements[[/footnote]] wholesome Petting Zoo you can Feel Better^^TM^^ by petting everything we have in stock! Yes, **EVERYTHING**!//
[[/div]]
----
[[div style="font-family: 'Just Me Again Down Here', cursive; font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: -50px;"]]
**Our Critters:**
[[/div]]
[[tabview]]
[[tab SCP-6169]]
[[div class="my-content"]]
[[div style="font-size: 48px;"]]
//[[[SCP-6169]]]//
[[/div]]
[[include component:image-block
| name=6169.jpg
| caption=LOOK AT THAT FLUFF!
]]
//SCP-6169 is our very first fluffer. Created in the dark ages of MemeCon, this one's the pride and joy of Hungrypossum's Petting Zoo! With a friendly attitude and an even friendlier wool coat, it's no wonder that it's been a fan-favourite ever since its public release.//
[[/div]]
[[/tab]]
[[tab SCP-5273]]
[[div class="my-content"]]
[[div style="font-size: 48px;"]]
//[[[SCP-5273]]]//
[[/div]]
[[include component:image-block
| name=5273.PNG
| caption=How can you not pet this lil fella?
| align=left
]]
//Have you ever wanted to pet a **concept** ? Worry not, our Petting Zoo caters to each and every customer!
SCP-5273 was brought to our attention by fellow cryptozoologist [[*user Dr Golden]]. Its origins can be tracked, again, to MemeCon, temporarily going extinct and then coming back to life with a better petting potential!//
[[/div]]
[[/tab]]
[[tab SCP-5461]]
[[div class="my-content"]]
[[div style="font-size: 48px;"]]
//[[[SCP-5461]]]//
[[/div]]
[[include component:image-block
| name=5461.jpg
| caption=AWW YISS THAT'S THE STUFF
| width=auto
| align=center
]]
//"But hungrypossum, petting concepts is **so** 3 eons ago" you say? Fortunately, we have something for you too. With the latest advances in Petting Technology, now you can even pet RITUALS! That's right, and the prime example would be SCP-5461, a hefty chonker (despite the low word count) that just can't get enough of everyone's pets!//[[footnote]]Caution is advised when petting SCP-5461, as it tends to get overly excited and teleport people to extra-dimensional mountaintops. Hungrypossum's Petting Zoo's liability in such cases is limited to $4.20 and a homemade cheeseburger. [[/footnote]]
[[/div]]
[[/tab]]
[[tab SCP-5754]]
[[div class="my-content"]]
[[div style="font-size: 48px;"]]
//[[[SCP-5754]]]//
[[/div]]
[[include component:image-block
| name=5754.jpg
| caption=More is Better^^TM^^
]]
//Humans have their own version of Fur, and that is Hair. And since More Fur = More Fluff = More Fun, it only follows that More Hair = More Fun as well! [[span style="font-size: 60%"]]...I think? Maybe...[[/span]]//
[[/div]]
[[/tab]]
[[tab RECURSIVE]]
[[div class="my-content"]]
[[div style="font-size: 48px;"]]
//[[[hungrypossum-s-petting-zoo | Hungrypossum's Petting Zoo]]]//
[[/div]]
[[include component:image-block
| name=author_page.PNG
| caption=Wait, we've just been here...
| width=auto
| align=center
]]
//Everyone loves a good ol' recursive petting, right? ...Right? Um, ok, well this is awkward... Anyway, this here pal has decided that trying to be unique is too much of a hassle, and just went with what came naturally.//
[[/div]]
[[/tab]]
[[/tabview]]
